Subject: [PATCH 4.4 09/39] clk: samsung: exynos4: mark chipid clock as CLK_IGNORE_UNUSED
Date:   Mon, 12 Oct 2020 15:26:39 +0200
Message-Id: <20201012132628.593731666@linuxfoundation.org>
